entries.content: Chose to implement quantum-inspired algorithms for parallel processing in the consciousness module
The GLYPH symbolic communication system enables loose coupling between modules while maintaining semantic richness
Memory folds preserve causal relationships better than traditional key-value stores. The emotional vectors add crucial context for decision replay.
How can we measure bio-symbolic coherence above 100%? Is this a quantum superposition effect?
Every major breakthrough happens after a period of confusion and experimentation. The 'dream' phase seems essential for innovation.
